```graphql
type Query {
  getValue: StringApiResponse
}

type StringApiResponse {
  statusCode: String!
  message: String!
  timestamp: String!
  payload: Payload
}

type Payload {
  logo: String!
  name: LanguageSpecificContent!
  copyrightText: LanguageSpecificContent!
  help: String!
  termsAndCondition: String!
}

type LanguageSpecificContent {
  en: String!
  ja: String!
}
```

With the above schema, we can use a query like below:

```graphql
