 - *Second*, there was a problem with my database as it was changed during the development and not updated. So, the solution was dropping the table, and it&#39;s done by adding **create-drop** to the configuration file, in my case it&#39;s *application.properties*:
```
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop
```

